gdiagram (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of gDiagram (formerly gPlantUML)
  * Full PlantUML support (10+ diagram types)
  * Complete Mermaid support (4 diagram types):
    - Flowcharts with 11 node shapes
    - Sequence diagrams with notes and loops
    - State diagrams with special states
    - Class diagrams with relationships
  * Native Graphviz rendering (no Java or Node.js)
  * Real-time preview with syntax highlighting
  * Auto-format detection (.puml, .mmd)
  * Export to SVG, PNG, PDF
  * Multi-tab editing
  * Dark mode support

 -- gDiagram Developers <packerlschupfer@github.com>  Fri, 27 Dec 2025 14:00:00 +0000
